content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4009.23 - Refund only on presentation

State Regulations

No refunds of money paid for pari-mutuel tickets to be
made as directed by this Subchapter shall be made except upon the presentation
and surrender of the tickets. Notes
